ISLAMABAD, Feb 12 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi Monday congratulated Alexander Stubb on his election as President of Finland.
The president, in a post on X, said, “Congratulations to Alexander Stubb on his election as President of Finland. Look forward to working together to further advance our longstanding and friendly relations, and growing cooperation in education, green energy transition and technical & vocational training.”
